        "scenario": "Onfido returns unexpected/malformed responses",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "SHOULD-HAVE: Defensive deserialization with clear error logging. Do not let a parsing exception produce an unhandled 500 — map it to a retryable KYC-pending state."
