        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "MUST-HAVE: Since Onfido SLA (99.9%) < internal SLA (99.95%), the architecture must decouple registration availability from Onfido availability. The only viable path is async/deferred KYC with a provisional registration state."
